WEBVTT

01:54.479 --> 01:55.350
Your Majesty,

01:55.870 --> 01:56.680
you

01:57.120 --> 01:58.640
summoned me?

02:10.190 --> 02:11.030
Brother,

02:12.080 --> 02:13.340
what's wrong with you?

02:14.560 --> 02:15.430
I

02:16.120 --> 02:17.910
have been sitting here for too long.

02:17.910 --> 02:19.310
My legs are a little numb.

02:19.840 --> 02:21.680
No matter how busy
you are with state affairs,

02:21.680 --> 02:23.880
you still need to get up and move around.

02:25.190 --> 02:26.280
Let me help you up.

02:26.470 --> 02:27.280
Take a few steps.

02:27.280 --> 02:27.870
No need. Come.

02:27.870 --> 02:28.470
No need.

02:28.470 --> 02:29.600
Slow down, brother.

02:30.280 --> 02:31.360
Slow down.

02:32.430 --> 02:33.430
Be careful.

02:36.590 --> 02:37.240
Brother.

02:37.470 --> 02:38.240
What is it?

02:38.560 --> 02:40.280
When you fell from the rooftop that night,

02:40.280 --> 02:41.880
you didn’t get hurt, did you?

02:42.750 --> 02:44.590
Fell from the rooftop?

02:45.030 --> 02:46.829
How could that possibly hurt me?

02:46.870 --> 02:47.430
That's good.

02:47.430 --> 02:49.490
Don’t you remember when we were kids?

02:49.590 --> 02:50.400
Every day

02:51.150 --> 02:52.480
we were climbing trees,

02:52.630 --> 02:53.690
jumping off roofs,

02:53.710 --> 02:55.360
and running all over the place—

02:55.360 --> 02:56.680
when did I get hurt?

02:57.430 --> 02:58.280
Ridiculous.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.590
Then your waist...

03:00.360 --> 03:01.080
I forgot.

03:01.150 --> 03:02.950
It's numb from sitting too long.

03:03.280 --> 03:03.590
Right.

03:03.590 --> 03:04.590
Numb from sitting too long.

03:04.590 --> 03:06.050
That time was an accident.

03:06.590 --> 03:08.590
You must not tell our eldest sister.

03:09.520 --> 03:10.320
I understand.

03:11.840 --> 03:12.590
An accident.

03:13.310 --> 03:14.400
Whatever you say,

03:14.400 --> 03:15.240
goes.

03:15.960 --> 03:17.560
You don't believe me, do you?

03:18.190 --> 03:19.430
If you don't believe me, let's go again.

03:19.430 --> 03:20.840
I'll definitely land on my feet.

03:20.840 --> 03:21.750
Brother,

03:22.240 --> 03:23.960
it's still bright outside.

03:24.310 --> 03:25.120
How about

03:25.520 --> 03:26.120
tonight?

03:28.710 --> 03:30.190
I can't go

03:30.190 --> 03:31.560
tonight.

03:32.000 --> 03:34.460
My eldest sister
is coming to see me tonight.

03:35.150 --> 03:36.430
The Eldest Princess?

03:36.430 --> 03:38.190
Then there's nothing I can do.

03:38.190 --> 03:39.120
I almost forgot.

03:39.400 --> 03:40.800
Xiao Chi and I arranged to drink

03:40.800 --> 03:42.079
in our bamboo forest.

03:42.750 --> 03:44.150
Then I will take my leave.

03:44.750 --> 03:46.150
You two brats

03:46.840 --> 03:48.400
are going drinking without me?

03:48.400 --> 03:49.910
Do you mean

03:49.910 --> 03:51.440
you can go with us, brother?

03:52.000 --> 03:54.360
Didn't I just say I can't go tonight?

03:54.560 --> 03:56.560
My eldest sister is coming to see me.

03:56.960 --> 03:58.190
That's a pity.

03:58.560 --> 04:00.360
Since you can't join us, brother,

04:00.360 --> 04:02.490
we'll just have to drink by ourselves.

04:02.560 --> 04:03.190
Wait.

04:03.710 --> 04:05.030
I'll take my leave.

04:05.030 --> 04:05.710
Wait.

04:06.840 --> 04:07.630
What a pity.

04:07.630 --> 04:08.470
Wait a minute.

04:09.590 --> 04:10.430
How about you

04:11.360 --> 04:12.710
drinking here?

04:20.240 --> 04:22.100
All I do every day is eat and sleep.

04:22.430 --> 04:24.310
I miss the sand seas of Changmo.

04:24.800 --> 04:25.630
How about

04:25.870 --> 04:27.040
we go out for a walk?

04:27.430 --> 04:29.240
Will General Xiao agree to that?

04:29.240 --> 04:31.100
I heard Xiao Chi isn't here today.

04:31.360 --> 04:32.600
Let's sneak out.

04:33.600 --> 04:34.400
Let's go then.

04:51.560 --> 04:52.310
Jin Xi,

04:52.630 --> 04:53.159
let's go.

05:01.600 --> 05:02.390
Princess,

05:04.630 --> 05:05.760
where are you going?

05:06.750 --> 05:08.160
We are just looking around.

05:08.160 --> 05:09.090
Looking around?

05:09.120 --> 05:09.720
I think

05:09.950 --> 05:11.510
you are about to leave, Princess.

05:11.510 --> 05:13.000
It's lunchtime.

05:13.190 --> 05:15.630
I brought you lunch myself.

05:15.750 --> 05:17.280
Please go back to your room.

05:17.560 --> 05:18.560
Don't run around.

05:19.600 --> 05:21.720
So we are not here
for a political marriage—

05:21.720 --> 05:23.600
we came to the General's Mansion
to sit in prison.

05:23.600 --> 05:24.120
No.

05:24.430 --> 05:25.600
She makes sense.

05:27.430 --> 05:28.290
Physician Han,

05:30.830 --> 05:32.800
General Xiao is busy outside every day.

05:32.800 --> 05:34.950
It's one thing that he can't stay in
the manor with the princess,

05:34.950 --> 05:37.510
but she can't even go out for a walk?

05:38.240 --> 05:39.120
No.

05:39.270 --> 05:41.240
I'm just afraid

05:41.240 --> 05:42.360
it's not safe on the streets.

05:42.360 --> 05:43.800
What could be unsafe?

05:44.120 --> 05:45.390
Being cooped up in the room every day

05:45.390 --> 05:46.790
will drive anyone crazy.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.240
As it happens,

05:48.240 --> 05:49.510
I'm going out today.

05:50.120 --> 05:51.560
The princess can be with me.

05:51.560 --> 05:52.270
Yeah.

05:52.630 --> 05:53.510
With Physician Han here,

05:53.510 --> 05:54.600
you don't have to worry.

05:54.600 --> 05:55.040
Let's go.

05:55.040 --> 05:55.750
Wait.

05:56.430 --> 05:58.159
Don't worry, Vice General Xu,

05:58.310 --> 06:00.190
we will come back safely.

06:00.600 --> 06:01.870
Don't worry?

06:03.830 --> 06:05.390
We don’t have streets
this lively and bustling

06:05.390 --> 06:07.040
back in Changmo.

06:07.870 --> 06:10.270
So you should come out
and walk around more.

06:10.430 --> 06:12.630
Crowds inevitably lead to trouble.

06:13.510 --> 06:14.480
Physician Han,

06:14.480 --> 06:15.310
the sachet.

06:20.560 --> 06:21.190
Bro.

06:21.360 --> 06:21.870
Look at

06:22.040 --> 06:23.240
that girl over there.

06:24.720 --> 06:26.310
What a small world.

06:26.830 --> 06:28.390
The one next to her looks pretty good too.

06:28.390 --> 06:28.800
Bro,

06:28.800 --> 06:31.310
let's not mess with that girl for now.

06:31.310 --> 06:32.750
Yeah, Bro, I'm scared.

06:33.510 --> 06:34.560
You coward.

06:34.560 --> 06:35.390
I don't believe

06:35.390 --> 06:37.630
anyone will come to help them today.

06:38.120 --> 06:38.560
Boss,

06:38.560 --> 06:39.190
I want two.

06:39.870 --> 06:40.630
Okay, miss.

06:49.360 --> 06:49.950
Jin Xi!

06:51.800 --> 06:52.750
There are pinwheels here.

06:52.750 --> 06:53.270
Miss,

06:53.270 --> 06:54.070
pick one.

06:54.510 --> 06:55.040
Let's go.

06:56.950 --> 06:58.240
Which one do you like?

06:59.120 --> 07:00.180
Let me see this one.

07:04.120 --> 07:05.180
What are you doing?

07:05.240 --> 07:06.800
These two girls

07:06.920 --> 07:07.950
are pretty nice, aren’t they?

07:07.950 --> 07:09.560
None of your business.

07:10.310 --> 07:11.800
What do you think

07:12.070 --> 07:13.720
of me?

07:16.720 --> 07:18.050
One offered herself up?

07:18.750 --> 07:19.920
Oh, very nice.

07:19.920 --> 07:20.450
Let's go.

07:20.720 --> 07:21.870
This girl is great.

07:22.270 --> 07:22.430
Go.

07:22.430 --> 07:23.600
Hurry up.

07:27.310 --> 07:28.360
Keep up.

07:28.360 --> 07:29.630
Hurry up.

07:30.390 --> 07:31.040
Coming.

07:32.310 --> 07:33.190
Second Brother,

07:33.190 --> 07:34.190
where is this?

07:35.120 --> 07:36.250
You don't remember?

07:36.600 --> 07:37.860
I don't remember much.

07:39.190 --> 07:40.800
This is the bamboo forest

07:40.800 --> 07:42.360
you, Oldest Brother, and I planted

07:42.360 --> 07:44.240
before you went to Tianlang Pass.

07:44.830 --> 07:46.560
At that time, this bamboo forest

07:46.560 --> 07:48.000
wasn't even as tall as me.

07:48.159 --> 07:50.040
So how many years have you been gone?

07:50.040 --> 07:50.800
Come here.

07:53.430 --> 07:55.830
Since we're revisiting
our old haunt today,

07:55.830 --> 07:57.890
we must drink to our heart's content.

08:01.000 --> 08:03.000
Let me pour a drink for General Xiao.

08:03.600 --> 08:04.270
Then

08:04.270 --> 08:05.830
thank you, Lord Fei.

08:08.830 --> 08:10.490
But without big brother here,

08:11.000 --> 08:12.600
it feels a bit less exciting.

08:14.190 --> 08:15.950
Since His Majesty ascended the throne,

08:15.950 --> 08:18.880
he really has few opportunities
to leave the palace.

08:19.040 --> 08:19.900
How about this?

08:20.630 --> 08:21.360
In the future,

08:21.360 --> 08:22.690
we two will find a chance

08:22.920 --> 08:24.630
to secretly bring him here.

08:26.920 --> 08:27.360
Then

08:27.600 --> 08:28.720
let's toast to big brother.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.580
To big brother.

08:36.240 --> 08:39.770
Miss, come take a look at
these styles and see which one you like.

08:39.789 --> 08:40.720
Princess,

08:40.720 --> 08:42.380
these earrings suit you well.

08:42.750 --> 08:44.030
Very beautiful.

08:44.150 --> 08:45.150
Boss, wrap it up.

08:45.630 --> 08:47.160
You have great taste, miss.

08:47.720 --> 08:48.600
Physician Han,

08:48.960 --> 08:50.840
we traveled all the way
from Tianlang Pass,

08:50.840 --> 08:52.240
and you cured my illness.

08:52.550 --> 08:54.030
Let's not be strangers from now on.

08:54.030 --> 08:55.150
Call me Wanyu.

08:55.630 --> 08:57.960
Then I won't stand on ceremony, Princess.

08:58.320 --> 08:59.120
Wanyu.

08:59.750 --> 09:00.390
Yunling.

09:11.200 --> 09:12.800
This suits Jin Xi perfectly.

09:16.360 --> 09:17.510
Where is Jin Xi?

09:18.600 --> 09:20.260
I've been here the whole time.

09:25.000 --> 09:26.440
Jin Xi, turn around.

09:28.360 --> 09:29.750
Hurry up.

09:43.550 --> 09:44.750
You have great taste.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.840
We picked it together.

09:50.150 --> 09:50.680
Hurry up.

09:50.750 --> 09:52.030
There's more fun stuff ahead.

09:52.030 --> 09:52.560
Let's go.

09:53.200 --> 09:54.120
Excuse me.

09:55.240 --> 09:56.030
Thank you.

09:57.320 --> 09:58.150
Let's go.

10:09.390 --> 10:10.990
You’ve finally made it back,

10:11.080 --> 10:12.390
so don’t leave again.

10:18.910 --> 10:20.390
I’m used to life in the military camp.

10:20.390 --> 10:22.390
If I suddenly had to stay in the capital,

10:22.390 --> 10:24.320
I'm afraid I wouldn't be used to it.

10:26.510 --> 10:27.600
What if

10:27.840 --> 10:31.100
Physician Han also stayed in
the capital and didn't leave?

10:33.630 --> 10:34.750
She...

10:37.320 --> 10:39.200
She will probably take her brother

10:39.200 --> 10:40.200
back to Changmo.

10:40.630 --> 10:42.200
It's easy to make her stay.

10:45.320 --> 10:46.790
Just settle her down

10:47.240 --> 10:48.370
here in the capital.

10:50.150 --> 10:51.080
Second Brother,

10:52.030 --> 10:53.560
what are you talking about?

10:54.200 --> 10:55.330
I don't understand.

10:55.630 --> 10:56.890
You don't understand?

11:00.080 --> 11:01.440
Forget it then.

11:02.320 --> 11:04.870
As the Minister of Revenue, I have

11:05.320 --> 11:08.240
countless houses and fertile lands
under my control.

11:08.240 --> 11:09.100
How about this.

11:09.120 --> 11:10.270
After I go back,

11:10.360 --> 11:11.630
I will pick one

11:11.840 --> 11:13.570
and give it to her. Will that do?

11:17.150 --> 11:18.120
She

11:19.600 --> 11:21.840
is not the kind of person to seek comfort.

11:21.840 --> 11:23.120
This won't work,

11:23.120 --> 11:24.250
and that won't work.

11:25.390 --> 11:26.240
Tell me,

11:27.030 --> 11:27.960
what should I do?

11:30.150 --> 11:31.320
How would I know

11:32.000 --> 11:33.200
what she's thinking?

11:36.550 --> 11:37.680
Judging by the time,

11:38.000 --> 11:39.240
you should go back

11:39.240 --> 11:40.600
and let her treat you.

11:45.960 --> 11:47.200
Go back.

11:50.200 --> 11:51.030
You brat,

11:52.390 --> 11:55.120
do you think I don't know
what you're thinking?

11:57.600 --> 11:59.200
I brought you your medicine.

12:01.840 --> 12:03.300
You took the Princess out?

12:03.550 --> 12:06.150
She's been locked up
ever since she arrived in the capital.

12:06.150 --> 12:07.200
If you keep locking her up,

12:07.200 --> 12:08.200
she will go crazy.

12:08.200 --> 12:09.550
If anything happens to her,

12:09.550 --> 12:11.480
who will take the responsibility?

12:14.840 --> 12:16.360
I didn't think it through.

12:16.440 --> 12:17.700
It won't happen again.

12:21.120 --> 12:22.440
This is my duty.

12:22.720 --> 12:23.980
I hope you understand.

12:25.030 --> 12:25.840
Yeah.

12:32.360 --> 12:34.120
This mandarin duck embroidery
is quite nice.

12:34.120 --> 12:34.870
Right?

12:34.870 --> 12:36.030
It is quite nice.

12:36.440 --> 12:38.320
But as a young woman in Jinglan,

12:38.320 --> 12:39.630
aren’t you afraid people will gossip

12:39.630 --> 12:40.750
if you go around so openly

12:40.750 --> 12:42.350
with a mandarin duck sachet?

12:44.150 --> 12:47.080
Then I will just say
it was given to me by General Xiao.

12:50.790 --> 12:53.200
Well then,
since it’s reciprocity between courtesy,

12:53.200 --> 12:55.600
what should you give me in return?

12:57.240 --> 13:00.040
It's a waste of your talent
not to be a businessman.

13:01.390 --> 13:02.510
It's just a sachet.

13:02.600 --> 13:04.320
I'll give General Xiao one in return.

13:04.320 --> 13:05.790
But rest assured, General.

13:05.790 --> 13:08.480
Mine doesn't have lovebirds on it.

13:09.200 --> 13:10.630
I put a lot of herbs in it.

13:10.870 --> 13:12.750
It's great for preventing diseases.

13:12.750 --> 13:13.910
Please, General,

13:13.910 --> 13:15.550
make sure to keep it with you.

13:33.360 --> 13:34.120
My Lord,

13:34.320 --> 13:36.000
Xiao Chi wants to see you.

13:38.440 --> 13:41.320
So he actually thought of coming here.

13:43.750 --> 13:45.030
Let him in.

13:45.150 --> 13:45.720
Yes.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.320
Lord Zhang.

13:51.910 --> 13:53.080
General Xiao.

13:54.120 --> 13:55.390
What brings you

13:55.390 --> 13:57.320
here?

13:57.750 --> 14:00.240
Lord Zhang is the chief minister
of the court.

14:00.240 --> 14:01.750
Having returned from Tianlang Pass,

14:01.750 --> 14:03.600
naturally I came to pay my respects.

14:03.600 --> 14:04.630
In that case,

14:04.630 --> 14:06.720
if I don't invite you to sit,

14:06.790 --> 14:09.390
it would make me seem unreasonable.

14:09.390 --> 14:10.520
Please, have a seat.

14:16.320 --> 14:17.030
Come,

14:17.030 --> 14:18.200
General Xiao.

14:21.840 --> 14:22.910
General Xiao,

14:23.360 --> 14:24.720
you've come at a bad time.

14:24.720 --> 14:26.320
We're out of tea in the manor.

14:27.000 --> 14:27.670
No matter.

14:28.030 --> 14:28.960
I didn't come

14:29.360 --> 14:30.750
for tea today.

14:31.240 --> 14:32.370
I just didn't expect

14:32.480 --> 14:34.000
that Lord Zhang's massive manor

14:34.000 --> 14:35.240
would be out of water.

14:35.320 --> 14:36.550
How incorruptible.

14:36.550 --> 14:37.870
As an official,

14:37.870 --> 14:40.070
I serve the Emperor and the court above,

14:40.200 --> 14:41.960
and the common people below.

14:42.150 --> 14:44.440
As a childless widower,

14:45.000 --> 14:46.910
why would I need so much money?

14:46.910 --> 14:48.030
General Xiao,

14:48.030 --> 14:49.630
just say what you want to say.

14:49.630 --> 14:51.390
Don't delay me

14:51.840 --> 14:52.960
from my reading.

14:53.910 --> 14:55.240
Lord Zhang is straightforward.

14:55.240 --> 14:57.200
Then I'll get straight to the point.

14:57.200 --> 15:00.030
I wonder if Lord Zhang knows anything

15:01.000 --> 15:01.840
about the death of Judge Xue.

15:01.840 --> 15:02.960
Judge Xue?

15:05.000 --> 15:07.200
Judge Xue.

15:07.390 --> 15:09.630
Which Judge Xue are you talking about?

15:09.840 --> 15:11.080
The Judge Xue who

15:11.270 --> 15:13.790
presided over the Han family massacre.

15:14.550 --> 15:15.440
Oh,

15:17.030 --> 15:18.840
I think I remember.

15:20.360 --> 15:21.390
He's dead?

15:23.720 --> 15:25.390
But it's not surprising.

15:25.790 --> 15:27.550
We are all getting old.

15:27.750 --> 15:29.240
Birth, old age, sickness, and death

15:29.240 --> 15:31.720
are up to heaven, not ourselves.

15:31.720 --> 15:32.720
Lord Zhang,

15:34.320 --> 15:35.960
he was murdered.

15:37.960 --> 15:39.670
Murdered?

15:40.320 --> 15:42.670
Then you should hurry up and find

15:42.670 --> 15:44.440
the constables investigating the case.

15:44.440 --> 15:46.240
Why did you come to me?

15:46.600 --> 15:47.360
Do you

15:47.790 --> 15:49.150
suspect me?

15:49.630 --> 15:52.000
Then you have to produce evidence.

15:52.440 --> 15:53.910
How could I suspect

15:53.910 --> 15:55.640
the incorruptible Lord Zhang?

15:59.480 --> 16:00.360
General Xiao,

16:00.720 --> 16:01.790
what made you

16:02.000 --> 16:04.440
think of looking for Judge Xue?

16:05.670 --> 16:07.120
I wanted to ask about

16:07.120 --> 16:09.440
the details of the Han family massacre.

16:12.200 --> 16:14.840
That was many years ago.

16:15.840 --> 16:16.870
Does Lord Zhang

16:16.870 --> 16:18.630
know what happened back then?

16:19.840 --> 16:21.360
Many years ago,

16:21.960 --> 16:23.840
the entire population of Jinglan

16:24.150 --> 16:26.150
was suffering from a severe plague.

16:26.630 --> 16:28.000
Every household hung white banners.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.660
There were dead in every home.

16:29.790 --> 16:32.000
It was truly unbearable to see.

16:32.150 --> 16:34.000
As for the Han family,

16:34.000 --> 16:35.910
I know a little.

16:35.960 --> 16:37.910
It’s said they administered
the wrong medicine,

16:37.910 --> 16:39.000
which led to patient deaths,

16:39.000 --> 16:41.860
and that’s why they were executed
as a whole family.

16:42.550 --> 16:44.150
If anyone from the Han family

16:44.630 --> 16:46.150
managed to escape

16:46.150 --> 16:47.840
that massacre back then,

16:47.840 --> 16:50.440
they should reflect deeply on themselves.

16:50.630 --> 16:53.030
See if it was heaven's mercy

16:53.030 --> 16:55.240
or if they got what they deserved.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.120
General Xiao,

17:03.630 --> 17:04.720
if

17:04.720 --> 17:06.200
there is nothing else,

17:07.200 --> 17:09.349
I would like to rest.

17:10.920 --> 17:11.510
Alright.

17:13.200 --> 17:14.069
In that case,

17:14.790 --> 17:16.990
I will not bother Lord Zhang any longer.

17:17.000 --> 17:18.510
Take care, General Xiao.

17:25.640 --> 17:27.790
This Xiao Chi.

17:35.110 --> 17:35.960
Princess.

17:36.400 --> 17:37.510
Jin Xi,

17:37.510 --> 17:38.400
where did you go?

17:38.400 --> 17:39.550
Why are you so late?

17:40.400 --> 17:42.640
I thought the night was lovely,

17:42.640 --> 17:44.240
so we could have a drink.

17:44.830 --> 17:45.640
Yes.

17:46.440 --> 17:47.310
Today

17:47.310 --> 17:49.550
is Changmo's annual Sand Festival.

17:50.000 --> 17:52.860
In previous years,
I always spent it with my father.

17:53.310 --> 17:54.160
This year...

17:54.160 --> 17:55.000
Right.

17:55.400 --> 17:57.110
Today is the annual
Sand Sacrifice Festival.

17:57.110 --> 17:58.440
We should drink

17:58.440 --> 17:59.110
and dance.

18:01.200 --> 18:02.400
We have wine.

18:02.440 --> 18:03.160
How about this?

18:03.160 --> 18:04.240
You have a drink first.

18:04.240 --> 18:06.310
I'll go invite Physician Han over,

18:06.550 --> 18:08.280
and we can celebrate together.

18:08.590 --> 18:09.590
That sounds good.

18:15.750 --> 18:16.550
Well,

18:19.270 --> 18:20.400
you practice first.

18:20.510 --> 18:22.270
I'll go get Physician Han now.

18:22.590 --> 18:23.480
Okay.

19:15.720 --> 19:16.520
What's wrong?

19:17.590 --> 19:18.720
Why did you stop dancing?

19:18.720 --> 19:19.310
I...

19:19.920 --> 19:21.830
I didn't expect anyone to come.

19:23.110 --> 19:24.920
You danced beautifully just now, Princess.

19:24.920 --> 19:25.590
I...

19:28.720 --> 19:30.980
It really makes me want to keep watching.

19:33.640 --> 19:35.350
Where did Jin Xi go?

19:36.640 --> 19:38.100
Who are you talking about?

19:38.110 --> 19:38.790
No one.

19:39.510 --> 19:41.590
I meant you were in a hurry last time,

19:41.590 --> 19:43.920
and said you'd tell me
your name this time.

19:43.920 --> 19:45.450
Why haven't you told me yet?

19:49.310 --> 19:50.440
I...

19:52.640 --> 19:54.720
If I tell her I am Liu Chu,

19:54.920 --> 19:56.250
that would be so boring.

19:57.240 --> 19:59.640
But who can I be right now?

20:01.000 --> 20:02.310
Didn't I say last time?

20:02.350 --> 20:04.030
My relationship with Xiao Chi

20:04.030 --> 20:05.920
is as close as brothers.

20:06.240 --> 20:08.240
Just now, seeing you dance so beautifully—

20:08.240 --> 20:09.550
it was like a fairy

20:09.960 --> 20:11.160
descending to earth.

20:11.440 --> 20:12.640
May I invite you

20:13.310 --> 20:14.030
for a drink?

20:17.790 --> 20:19.550
Why hasn't Jin Xi returned yet?

20:21.790 --> 20:23.520
Then I'll have a drink with you.

20:27.960 --> 20:29.200
I wonder

20:29.720 --> 20:31.830
how things will go for them tonight.

20:33.960 --> 20:35.590
No matter how it goes,

20:35.790 --> 20:37.790
it's good for them to interact more.

20:38.240 --> 20:39.550
If their bond grows,

20:40.440 --> 20:42.590
the peace between our countries will last.

20:42.590 --> 20:43.830
How troublesome.

20:44.400 --> 20:45.030
In this world,

20:45.030 --> 20:47.230
there are far more troublesome things.

20:47.830 --> 20:48.590
Sometimes,

20:48.920 --> 20:51.450
I really just want to kill Liu Chu
with my sword

20:52.000 --> 20:54.000
and take his head back
to report my mission.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.240
You can't kill Liu Chu.

20:55.240 --> 20:56.720
Remember your mission

20:56.880 --> 20:58.070
is to protect the Princess

20:58.070 --> 21:00.270
and facilitate the marriage alliance.

21:00.590 --> 21:02.200
Even if Liu Chu deserves to die,

21:02.200 --> 21:03.590
how and when he dies

21:03.750 --> 21:05.210
is the King Mo's business.

21:05.960 --> 21:07.160
Don't take any risks.

21:11.510 --> 21:13.510
Liu Chu and Xiao Chi are my brothers.

21:14.510 --> 21:15.590
If one day

21:16.200 --> 21:18.000
they really must die,

21:18.640 --> 21:19.590
I hope

21:21.590 --> 21:23.350
I'm the one to kill them.

21:24.720 --> 21:25.830
You seem

21:26.240 --> 21:27.590
different from before.

21:28.240 --> 21:29.640
You're overthinking it.

21:29.920 --> 21:31.050
I've never changed.

21:34.400 --> 21:35.790
So you've

21:36.030 --> 21:37.960
lived in Changmo since you were little.

21:37.960 --> 21:38.750
Yeah.

21:39.590 --> 21:40.750
Ever since I can remember,

21:40.750 --> 21:42.640
I grew up by my father's side.

21:43.030 --> 21:44.440
Other than my father,

21:44.960 --> 21:46.830
I rarely saw other men.

21:49.960 --> 21:51.350
Changmo?

21:51.750 --> 21:53.200
What kind of place is it?

21:53.590 --> 21:55.110
Our Changmo,

21:55.310 --> 21:56.790
is a wonderful place.

21:57.440 --> 21:58.960
The vast yellow sands

21:59.030 --> 22:00.480
stretch endlessly.

22:00.790 --> 22:03.270
That little oasis in the yellow sand

22:03.400 --> 22:04.830
is just like

22:05.830 --> 22:08.030
as bright as the stars.

22:09.640 --> 22:11.240
Since it's such a nice place,

22:11.400 --> 22:13.260
there must be a lot of good things.

22:13.750 --> 22:14.830
Mm-hmm.

22:16.000 --> 22:18.330
Although the yellow sand is magnificent,

22:18.550 --> 22:19.960
our resources

22:19.960 --> 22:22.270
are indeed not as abundant as Jinglan's.

22:24.750 --> 22:26.160
If...

22:26.830 --> 22:28.440
If I were Liu Chu,

22:28.590 --> 22:29.920
I would definitely hope

22:30.110 --> 22:31.350
our two countries could be on good terms

22:31.350 --> 22:32.590
and open trade routes.

22:32.590 --> 22:35.390
We could send good things
from Jinglan to Changmo,

22:35.590 --> 22:38.310
and let the people of Changmo
come here to do business.

22:38.310 --> 22:42.040
This way, the relationship
between our countries would be closer,

22:42.200 --> 22:44.510
and life would be more prosperous.

22:46.590 --> 22:47.680
And if

22:47.880 --> 22:50.160
anyone dares to invade Changmo,

22:50.480 --> 22:52.590
I will definitely lead troops into battle

22:52.590 --> 22:54.250
and wipe them out completely.

22:59.000 --> 22:59.880
Why

23:00.440 --> 23:01.440
are you laughing?

23:02.830 --> 23:03.830
Nothing.

23:08.110 --> 23:09.240
You

23:09.550 --> 23:11.480
are here for a political marriage?

23:11.510 --> 23:13.440
You haven't even seen
what Liu Chu looks like.

23:13.440 --> 23:15.160
Why do you want to marry him?

23:15.790 --> 23:18.030
What if he's an old man,

23:18.030 --> 23:18.880
or

23:19.200 --> 23:20.440
ugly?

23:20.790 --> 23:21.720
He won't be.

23:22.240 --> 23:23.680
My father told me

23:24.110 --> 23:26.310
Liu Chu is only a few years older than me.

23:26.510 --> 23:27.550
Besides,

23:29.440 --> 23:31.350
I've seen his portrait.

23:34.000 --> 23:35.640
You've seen his portrait?

23:39.920 --> 23:41.310
Then how do you think

23:41.640 --> 23:44.510
he compares

23:45.920 --> 23:46.750
to me?

23:48.160 --> 23:50.440
You are a handsome man,

23:51.440 --> 23:53.160
but in my heart,

23:53.720 --> 23:55.200
there is only Liu Chu.

23:57.400 --> 23:59.330
What exactly do you love about him?

23:59.440 --> 24:01.240
My father says he is

24:01.960 --> 24:03.550
wise and mighty,

24:03.720 --> 24:04.830
magnanimous,

24:05.200 --> 24:06.790
a blessing to the people,

24:06.960 --> 24:09.490
and loves his subjects
like his own children.

24:10.110 --> 24:11.110
Besides,

24:11.440 --> 24:13.310
on my way to the capital,

24:13.510 --> 24:15.240
I saw the people living in peace

24:15.510 --> 24:16.970
and the streets bustling.

24:17.240 --> 24:19.000
It proves my father didn't lie to me.

24:19.000 --> 24:20.590
Liu Chu is a good king.

24:21.510 --> 24:22.350
I...

24:25.720 --> 24:26.550
He...

24:27.160 --> 24:29.510
He can't be that good, right?

24:29.750 --> 24:30.720
Come, let me toast you again.

24:30.720 --> 24:31.050
Come.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.310
Then

24:38.960 --> 24:40.880
how can you be sure

24:41.440 --> 24:43.840
that he will love you
as much as you love him?

24:44.920 --> 24:46.400
My father told me

24:46.640 --> 24:48.240
we are a match made in heaven,

24:48.640 --> 24:50.400
destined by fate.

24:50.750 --> 24:52.950
He will definitely fall in love with me.

24:55.510 --> 24:57.200
That makes some sense.

24:57.830 --> 24:58.590
In that case,

25:00.000 --> 25:01.920
I wish you and Liu Chu

25:02.960 --> 25:04.920
a harmonious union
lasting a hundred years,

25:04.920 --> 25:06.180
early birth of an heir,

25:06.200 --> 25:07.160
growing old together,

25:07.160 --> 25:08.760
and a century of mutual love.

25:09.030 --> 25:10.110
Then I wish you

25:10.640 --> 25:12.310
to find your beloved soon.

25:13.960 --> 25:17.000
Actually, I think I already have.

25:33.640 --> 25:34.790
Princess,

25:35.070 --> 25:36.160
that dance earlier

25:36.640 --> 25:37.830
was beautiful.

25:38.830 --> 25:39.790
Could you

25:41.790 --> 25:42.590
dance again?

25:43.550 --> 25:45.200
I'll pass on the dancing.

25:45.350 --> 25:46.510
It's getting late today,

25:46.510 --> 25:48.590
and it's not appropriate
for us to drink here.

25:48.590 --> 25:50.270
I'm going to find Jin Xi first.

26:33.480 --> 26:34.510
Why are you here?

26:38.550 --> 26:39.920
I wanted to take a walk,

26:40.440 --> 26:41.970
and somehow I ended up here.

26:43.920 --> 26:44.750
Did you

26:45.240 --> 26:46.750
remember something?

26:48.920 --> 26:51.160
Was I supposed to remember something?

26:53.750 --> 26:54.950
This river is so deep.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.400
If you fall in,

26:56.400 --> 26:57.590
we'll both die.

27:01.510 --> 27:02.110
I

27:02.110 --> 27:03.160
didn't mean that.

27:07.790 --> 27:09.790
Thank you for helping me find my brother

27:09.790 --> 27:11.720
and for investigating Lord Zhang.

27:11.830 --> 27:12.720
It's nothing.

27:14.030 --> 27:15.110
Actually,

27:16.240 --> 27:18.160
things might not go that smoothly.

27:18.160 --> 27:20.160
If it really comes to a point
where the investigation can’t continue

27:20.160 --> 27:21.620
there's nothing we can do.

27:21.830 --> 27:23.160
But before that,

27:23.790 --> 27:24.960
I won't give up.

27:28.920 --> 27:30.400
When I was young,

27:30.680 --> 27:31.880
I met a girl

27:32.030 --> 27:33.690
who said the same thing as you.

27:36.110 --> 27:38.000
Is the girl you mentioned

27:38.310 --> 27:39.440
me?

27:40.920 --> 27:42.000
What if I said yes?

27:45.400 --> 27:46.550
I'm just kidding.

27:49.750 --> 27:50.830
I'm serious.

28:07.350 --> 28:08.160
Brother.

28:08.960 --> 28:10.090
You wanted to see me?

28:10.510 --> 28:11.110
Yes.

28:12.440 --> 28:13.240
Second Brother,

28:13.240 --> 28:15.240
has Xiao Chi received

28:15.240 --> 28:16.480
any news from

28:16.480 --> 28:17.880
Tianlang Pass recently?

28:17.920 --> 28:19.790
How would I know?

28:19.790 --> 28:21.550
But since Third Brother
hasn't reported anything,

28:21.550 --> 28:23.350
it means the border is peaceful.

28:23.550 --> 28:24.280
Makes sense.

28:25.590 --> 28:29.350
It seems relations
between Jinglan and Changmo are improving,

28:29.350 --> 28:30.160
doesn’t it?”

28:30.830 --> 28:33.920
Now that the Princess has just
arrived in the capital,

28:34.200 --> 28:36.200
it has brought peace to the borders.

28:36.790 --> 28:38.400
When the marriage alliance is completed,

28:38.400 --> 28:39.750
Jinglan and Changmo

28:39.750 --> 28:41.550
will surely be at peace forever.

28:43.550 --> 28:45.750
You are temporarily
in charge of the Ministry of Rites.

28:45.750 --> 28:46.960
So when do you think

28:46.960 --> 28:48.590
the ceremony should be held?

28:49.880 --> 28:50.720
Brother,

28:50.920 --> 28:52.830
I have long been prepared for this.

28:52.830 --> 28:54.510
I've been carrying this
until it's almost worn out.

28:54.510 --> 28:55.400
Come on.

28:55.400 --> 28:56.510
This is the Imperial Astronomical
Bureau’s auspicious dates

28:56.510 --> 28:58.750
for the next six months.

28:59.200 --> 29:00.800
Please take a look, brother.

29:09.200 --> 29:12.270
I was thinking that good relations
between Jinglan and Changmo

29:12.270 --> 29:13.600
will benefit the people

29:13.750 --> 29:15.200
and ensure

29:15.200 --> 29:16.510
everlasting peace.

29:17.310 --> 29:18.350
Whatever Your Majesty does

29:18.350 --> 29:21.210
is definitely
for the sake of the people of Jinglan.

29:21.480 --> 29:22.160
Of course.

29:22.350 --> 29:23.000
Of course.

29:24.000 --> 29:25.330
So which day do you think

29:25.440 --> 29:26.920
is the best?

29:27.440 --> 29:29.700
Brother, these are all auspicious days.

29:29.790 --> 29:31.550
But if you ask me,

29:31.550 --> 29:33.030
it should be as soon as possible,

29:33.030 --> 29:34.630
like the tenth of next month.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.000
So soon?

29:37.000 --> 29:37.720
The Princess of Changmo

29:37.720 --> 29:39.550
has been in the capital for a while.

29:39.550 --> 29:41.160
If we delay any longer,

29:41.160 --> 29:43.240
I'm afraid Changmo will be suspicious.

29:43.240 --> 29:46.920
But what about the many matters
regarding the marriage ceremony?

29:47.750 --> 29:49.240
Rest assured, Brother.

29:49.240 --> 29:50.830
Since returning to the capital,

29:50.830 --> 29:52.400
I've already started

29:52.400 --> 29:54.110
planning and arranging it.

29:56.240 --> 29:58.240
No wonder you’re my second brother.

29:58.720 --> 29:59.510
Good.

30:00.240 --> 30:01.400
Then,

30:01.960 --> 30:03.350
Brother, we...

30:10.240 --> 30:11.720
B-Brother.

30:12.480 --> 30:14.350
I'm done here.

30:15.350 --> 30:17.350
Go about your business.

30:19.550 --> 30:20.270
Then,

30:20.720 --> 30:22.320
Brother, I'll take my leave.

30:32.590 --> 30:33.920
So it seems

30:34.200 --> 30:35.720
Wanyue and Liu Chu

30:36.510 --> 30:38.790
are indeed a natural pair.

30:40.160 --> 30:42.310
If they were truly fond of each other,
that would be even better.

30:42.310 --> 30:44.590
Given the Princess's beauty and kindness,

30:44.590 --> 30:46.440
Liu Chu would surely fall into
that softness

30:46.440 --> 30:48.100
and be unable to free himself.

30:48.440 --> 30:49.400
Remember

30:49.590 --> 30:52.110
this is just one part of our many plans.

30:52.830 --> 30:54.550
From now on,

30:55.350 --> 30:57.240
keep a close eye on every step.

30:57.750 --> 30:58.550
I will.

31:03.310 --> 31:04.350
It hurts again?

31:05.830 --> 31:07.720
My heart aches.
